        <name>MonotonicMs</name>
        <qualifiedname>hf_time::MonotonicMs</qualifiedname>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Convenience milliseconds view of the same monotonic counter. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Implemented in terms of <computeroutput><ref refid="namespacehf__time_1a6bbd69949f8405073c7a495676c65d08" kindref="member">MonotonicUs()</ref></computeroutput> so the underlying timebase stays consistent across <computeroutput>Us</computeroutput> and <computeroutput>Ms</computeroutput> queries. Resolution is still 1 µs internally; only the unit conversion differs. </para>
